%F A076454 a(n) = n*(n+1)*(2*n^2-1)/2.
%F A076454 G.f.: x*(1+16*x+7*x^2)/(1-x)^5.
%F A076454 a(n) = 5*a(n-1)-10*a(n-2)+10*a(n-3)-5*a(n-4)+a(n-5), n>=6, with a(1)=1, a(2)=21, a(3)=102, a(4)=310, a(5)=735. - _L. Edson Jeffery_, Dec 30 2013
